Steps to create a component:

1. create a SFC (Single File Component) (*.vue)
2. Write your code
3. Component will accept props from parent component (where this component is being used)
4. To share data from Child / this component with parent component use this.$emit(eventName, data), second param is optional
5. To use a child component, import it locally / globally, register in the components object in script section
6. The emit custom event is called on the child component tag in the parent component, and can use and of its methods




